If you're working with very large cohorts

00:35:59.879 --> 00:36:02.199
and maybe a purchase order makes more sense for you,

00:36:02.959 --> 00:36:04.000
we're flexible there as well

00:36:04.000 --> 00:36:07.879
and can talk through your needs on a case-by-case basis.

00:36:07.879 --> 00:36:09.760
In each one, to set up ways

00:36:09.760 --> 00:36:11.199
to accommodate your student costs,

00:36:11.199 --> 00:36:14.399
there are three primary approaches.

00:36:14.399 --> 00:36:18.360
Either you can pay a $5 per student monthly fee

00:36:19.320 --> 00:36:20.800
for the student.

00:36:20.800 --> 00:36:23.600
You can have each student pay it for themselves

00:36:23.600 --> 00:36:26.800
or you can set up an account, again, through Stripe,

00:36:26.800 --> 00:36:29.239
through a credit card on the platform

00:36:29.239 --> 00:36:32.320
that only will go back to the usage within your space.

00:36:32.320 --> 00:36:35.040
So you would pay $15 for your instructor fee

00:36:35.040 --> 00:36:36.800
and then anything above that would just be

00:36:36.800 --> 00:36:40.679
based upon the compute hours used by students in your space.

00:36:42.120 --> 00:36:45.879
So again, I encourage you to go to posit.cloud,

00:36:45.879 --> 00:36:47.120
create a free account,

00:36:47.120 --> 00:36:48.639
play around with some of the functionality

00:36:48.639 --> 00:36:51.560
that we looked at today.

00:36:51.560 --> 00:36:55.280
And really, I think if you haven't tried teaching

00:36:55.280 --> 00:36:57.479
through a cloud-based system yet,

00:36:57.479 --> 00:36:59.159
you're in for a real treat

00:37:00.080 --> 00:37:01.199
the preparation it takes

00:37:01.199 --> 00:37:03.120
to get all of your content in one place

00:37:03.120 --> 00:37:04.919
and the ability to bring on students

00:37:04.919 --> 00:37:08.040
in a pretty seamless way.

00:37:08.040 --> 00:37:10.399
Thank you very much for attending this.

00:37:10.399 --> 00:37:12.719
Mine, thank you so much for joining us

00:37:12.719 --> 00:37:17.159
and giving your incredible and very practiced opinions

00:37:17.159 --> 00:37:20.080
on using posit.cloud for this type of education.

